{"tid":2325371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗少女扮「喪屍版安祖蓮娜祖莉」成網紅　被指鼓勵青少年腐化判監十年","createTime":"2020-12-14T13:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T14:11:49.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6268e51b6b3cbc28cc4a159110caae02d27a8a78","tid":2325371,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T13:50:38.000Z","msg":"圖：<br />\n<a href=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/c3d2e52752613e3e61aa315aae57203f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201214/_2020121418121020406.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fc3d2e52752613e3e61aa315aae57203f%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201214%2F_2020121418121020406.jpg&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7n5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=8c909495\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fc3d2e52752613e3e61aa315aae57203f%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201214%2F_2020121418121020406.jpg&h=4cf6ced4\" target=\"_blank\">https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/c3d2e52752613e3e61aa315aae57203f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201214/_2020121418121020406.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n《印度斯坦時報》報道，被稱為「僵屍版」安祖蓮娜祖莉的伊朗少女「塔巴爾」，因為經常在社交媒體上載模仿安祖蓮娜祖莉，但瘦骨嶙峋令人毛骨悚然的照片，遭到當局起訴，並判監十年。<br />\n<br />\n這名十九歲的伊朗少女以「塔巴爾」這個名字，在社交網站Instagram開設帳戶，經常上載自己酷似安祖蓮娜的「僵屍版」照片。她會「嘟起嘴」模仿安祖蓮娜的招牌厚唇，又經常以一臉憔悴，瘦骨嶙峋形象示人。<br />\n<br />\n曾否認整形的「塔巴爾」，以誇張的修圖效果，令五官呈現不自然狀態，怪異的形象令她聲名大噪，在人氣最高時有近五十萬追隨者。<br />\n<br />\n不過「塔巴爾」的舉動，就被伊朗當局視為褻瀆和不尊重伊斯蘭共和國，當局去年拘捕「塔巴爾」，控以煽動暴力以不正當方式賺取收入，和鼓勵青少年腐化等多項罪名。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416529&d=4UWfeJE2Id0Ic3Ynx8r7n5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=b80509de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416529&h=6f7948b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=416529</a>"},{"pid":"588659d5f251821d73e5a1a5a3185f7e0b8b361e","tid":2325371,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T13:57:32.000Z","msg":"單野上年已經有"},{"pid":"dfff33c6b4aa7fa66f7629a74a25446f75da1f75","tid":2325371,"uid":80624,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T13:58:52.000Z","msg":"如果極權可以係呢個世界消失就好"},{"pid":"5c69400e8a78f10354ddbd5c26abf0f3d82e015d","tid":2325371,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T13:59:48.000Z","msg":"原本都女神級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4171930485c97fac89d3d42a5f337fe2747d13","tid":2325371,"uid":210140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"咁都有得拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然係幾恐怖下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710225a86d31d4c1c59f8dde9c9647e2642baeda","tid":2325371,"uid":324629,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff4171930485c97fac89d3d42a5f337fe2747d13","tid":2325371,"uid":210140,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"咁都有得拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然係幾恐怖下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T14:00:44.000Z","msg":"極權做得嘅嘢無嘢係你諗唔到"},{"pid":"e79796efd13e9a44a6693f618bb52a9b1bbf4641","tid":2325371,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T14:03:16.000Z","msg":"女權撚幾時出下聲?<br />\n中東國家迫害得女人最勁  同時女權撚就最睇唔到"},{"pid":"9b40bcd65405692cf4bb6cfcbfbee37f77952a2d","tid":2325371,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e79796efd13e9a44a6693f618bb52a9b1bbf4641","tid":2325371,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T14:03:16.000Z","msg":"女權撚幾時出下聲?